@startuml gkg_deploy_selfmanaged
!include gkg_common.puml

title Deployment: Self-Managed

' ===================================================================
' SELF-MANAGED-SPECIFIC: customer-provisioned ClickHouse
' ===================================================================
database "**ClickHouse**\nCode + SDLC data lake\n(customer-provisioned)" as ch #d09191

' Data layer connections
sdlc_idx --> ch : TCP native (write)
code_idx --> ch : TCP native (write)
query_eng --> ch : TCP native (read, parameterized SQL)

note bottom of module
  **ClickHouse:** Customer-provisioned and operated.
  Standard ClickHouse TCP/HTTP protocol.

  **Billing:** Per-seat add-on license.

  **Headwind:** Orbit is a non-Omnibus service.
  No established path for shipping new standalone
  services to Self-Managed. Oak initiative or
  equivalent needed.

  **Independent release:** Download new binary,
  restart. No monolith coordination.
end note

@enduml
